        <p>
          Semantic tags like <code>&lt;header&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;main&gt;</code>, and 
          <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> give meaning to content, making it easier for assistive 
          technologies and search engines to understand your page.
        </p>
